1
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Adapted from the story of the
same title by author Ku Xuan</font>

2
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}from Chinese Qidian Website of Yuewen
Group The Daily Life of the Immortal King</font>

3
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuan, come here.</font>

4
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daddy got you something.</font>

5
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da!</font>

6
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hehe.</font>

7
00:00:45,330 --> 00:00:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally got my writer's fee.</font>

8
00:00:48,270 --> 00:00:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spent a lot</font>

9
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">asking the Spirit Sword 4S Shop
to make it for you.</font>

10
00:00:54,270 --> 00:00:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you like it?</font>

11
00:01:04,020 --> 00:01:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's useless, dad.</font>

12
00:01:05,330 --> 00:01:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ordinary Spirit Swords can't handle
Wang Nuan's Spiritual Energy.</font>

13
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing...</font>

14
00:01:13,850 --> 00:01:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm putting it back together</font>

15
00:01:15,770 --> 00:01:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and asking the 4S shop to accept
unconditional returns within 7 days.</font>

16
00:01:20,810 --> 00:01:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alas.</font>

17
00:01:21,770 --> 00:01:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen other kids have Spirit Swords
by their side day and night since birth,</font>

18
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and nurturing sword spirits.</font>

19
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't let Nuan
fall behind at the starting line.</font>

20
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad. Mom. Leave the Spirit Sword to me.</font>

21
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The Daily Life of the Immortal King 5</font>

22
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Episode 9: Making
a Sword Spirit for Little Sister</font>

23
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go inside.</font>

24
00:03:24,650 --> 00:03:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prisoner is taken to the cell.</font>

25
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Headquarters got it.</font>

26
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

27
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all remember this.</font>

28
00:03:33,230 --> 00:03:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I break free,
every last one of you will die.</font>

29
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What bad timing.</font>

30
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First Prison just tightened security.</font>

31
00:03:59,850 --> 00:04:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What took you so long?</font>

32
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave you chances,</font>

33
00:04:13,810 --> 00:04:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you just couldn't get it done.</font>

34
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bai Zhe, you...</font>

35
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Sword Immortal Fan Rui's disciple,</font>

36
00:04:24,530 --> 00:04:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you'd know where the Demon Sword is.</font>

37
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think I'd tell you?</font>

38
00:04:32,690 --> 00:04:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we make a deal?</font>

39
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need.</font>

40
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lead the way.</font>

41
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Lord Bai Zhe.</font>

42
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nurturing a Sword Spirit 
is a long-term process.</font>

43
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Ling, if your sister 
wants a Sword Spirit,</font>

44
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she's gotta practice 
swordplay day and night,</font>

45
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and form a bond with the Spirit Sword.</font>

46
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And wait until your sister
comes of age, the Sword Spirit</font>

47
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will be summoned from
the Sword Spirit Mystic Realm.</font>

48
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sword Spirit Mystic Realm?</font>

49
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly.</font>

50
00:05:40,220 --> 00:05:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not go to the Sword Spirit
Mystic Realm to find one now?</font>

51
00:05:46,030 --> 00:05:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sword Spirit Mystic Realm's
entrance is right here.</font>

52
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it only opens automatically
every 2,000 years.</font>

53
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next opening is 
still 1,000 years away.</font>

54
00:05:58,170 --> 00:05:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to go to all that trouble.</font>

55
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

56
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, they can be one?</font>

57
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:25,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! This is so wild!</font>

58
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who said this peachwood sword was weak?</font>

59
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This peachwood sword is freaking awesome!</font>

60
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My respects, Sword Master.</font>

61
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going in.</font>

62
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alright.</font>

63
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This... This is the legendary...</font>

64
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sword Spirit Mystic Realm.</font>

65
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:01,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is my first time</font>

66
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">seeing someone going inside so directly.</font>

67
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then,</font>

68
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you pushed your Master off
the Cliff of Enlightenment.</font>

69
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, this's also where
the Demon Sword's spirit was sealed.</font>

70
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step back.</font>

71
00:08:09,420 --> 00:08:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

72
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see how long you can last.</font>

73
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My lord, it's time.</font>

74
00:08:35,470 --> 00:08:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a Demon Sword, it's mine now.</font>

75
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the inner 
world of the Sword Mound.</font>

76
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did Sword Spirit Mystic 
Realm become like this?</font>

77
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah?</font>

78
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

79
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last time I entered, there 
were many small Sword Spirits.</font>

80
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did they all disappear now?</font>

81
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sword Master, I'll take care of this.</font>

82
00:09:38,170 --> 00:09:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such a strong, intense vibe.</font>

83
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah!</font>

84
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is there such a vicious 
Sword Spirit here?</font>

85
00:09:58,330 --> 00:09:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh!</font>

86
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you... Aren't you shocked at all?</font>

87
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gotten used to it.</font>

88
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So these little guys 
were all hiding from it,</font>

89
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they didn't come out.</font>

90
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuan.</font>

91
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's going to rain soon.</font>

92
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go inside.</font>

93
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are Sword Spirit infants?</font>

94
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

95
00:10:56,330 --> 00:10:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sword Spirits can take human form,</font>

96
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">bestial form, or even plant form.</font>

97
00:11:00,190 --> 00:11:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After having the Spiritual 
Aura from nature,</font>

98
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Sword Spirit infants
evolve into different forms.</font>

99
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems Master Ling killed 
that fierce creature,</font>

100
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they finally dared to show up.</font>

101
00:11:13,170 --> 00:11:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That vicious Sword Spirit beast</font>

102
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">devoured plenty of these little guys
over the years, so it got so fat.</font>

103
00:11:18,540 --> 00:11:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So itchy.</font>

104
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do that.</font>

105
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to pick one for my little sister.</font>

106
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you want to choose?</font>

107
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be afraid.</font>

108
00:12:20,770 --> 00:12:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found it.</font>

109
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hahahahaha.</font>

110
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hear my summons.</font>

111
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show yourself, Spirit of the Demon Sword.</font>

112
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

113
00:13:02,540 --> 00:13:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did it go?</font>

114
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

115
00:13:12,330 --> 00:13:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What...</font>

116
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening?</font>

117
00:13:16,730 --> 00:13:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to be my little 
sister's Sword Spirit?</font>

118
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute!</font>

119
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can this little guy really protect Nuan?</font>

120
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

121
00:13:36,210 --> 00:13:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

122
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone is summoning it.</font>

123
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not quite what I imagined,</font>

124
00:13:51,930 --> 00:13:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's the Sword Spirit 
of the Demon Sword.</font>

125
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Destroy this place.</font>

126
00:14:50,420 --> 00:14:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

127
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did it run away?</font>

128
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will be back.</font>

129
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It got teleported away
before the ceremony even ended,</font>

130
00:15:39,990 --> 00:15:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because Nuan summoned it.</font>

131
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My little sister is way crazier</font>

132
00:15:49,210 --> 00:15:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">than I ever was as a kid.</font>

